Title: What Did We Do?
Writer: Peter Nowalk (created by), Michael Foley, Erika Green Swafford, Erika Harrison (story editor)
Actors: Viola Davis, Billy Brown, Alfred Enoch, Jack Falahee
Plot: ADA Sinclair finally gets her biggest break yet in the Hapstall case - but it comes with a deadly consequence as the details of the night Annalise was shot are revealed, and her shooter is finally unmasked.
